java.lang.Cloneable
public class DataType
extends AstNode

(DataType base_type_name indir), (DataType array (ArrayType) indir), or (DataType function (FuncType) indir). Either a base type (primitive or structure) or a pointer to a base type indir is 0 if it is not a pointer Obsolete: If (IsArrayType()) then baseType is the element type of the array. Two public functions are used in the place of GenCode: GenTypeDecl() generates the type declaration GenDataDecl(String data_name) generates the data declaration
